children.name: Noah
children.decription: Noah's Ark

children.name: Abram
children.decription: Also known as Abraham

children.name: Ishmael
children.decription: The sons of Ishmael became the heads of twelve tribes

children.name: Eliphaz
children.decription: The ancestor of the tribes of Teman, Omar, Zephi, Gatam, Kenaz, Timna, and Amalek.

children.name: Reuel
children.decription: The ancestor of the tribes of Nahath, Zerah, Shammah, and Mizzah.

children.name: Jacob
children.decription: Ancestor of the twelve great tribes of Israel

children.name: Levi
children.decription: Ancestor of the line of High Priests

children.name: Asaph
children.decription: The leader of the second choir of the temple musicians appointed by David.

children.name: Azariah
children.decription: Served in the Temple which King Solomon built in Jerusalem.

children.name: Jehozadak
children.decription: Deported by King Nebuchadnezzar along with the other people of Judah and Jerusalem whom the Lord sent into exile.

children.name: Moses
children.decription: Led the Israelites out of Egypt

children.name: Heman
children.decription: The leader of the first choir of the temple musicians appointed by David.

children.name: Ethan
children.decription: The leader of the third choir of the temple musicians appointed by David.

children.name: Er
children.decription: Was so evil that the Lord killed him.

children.name: Nahshon
children.decription: A prominent man of the tribe of Judah.

children.name: David
children.decription: Israel's Greatest King

children.name: Shobal
children.decription: Founded Kiriath Jearim.

children.name: Ahumai
children.decription: Ancestor of the people who lived in Zorah

children.name: Lahad
children.decription: Ancestor of the people who lived in Zorah

children.name: Salma
children.decription: Founded Bethlehem

children.name: Hareph
children.decription: Founded Bethgader

children.name: Ashhur
children.decription: Founded the town of Tekoa.

children.name: Shaaph
children.decription: Founded the town of Madmannah.

children.name: Shevah
children.decription: Founded the towns of Machbenah and Gibea.

children.name: Segub
children.mother: Machir's daughter, the sister of Gilead

children.name: Jair
children.decription: Ruled twenty-three cities in the territory of Gilead.

children.name: Malchiel
children.decription: Founded the city of Birzaith.

children.name: Nimrod
children.decription: World's first great conqueror

children.name: Crete
children.decription: From whom the Philistines were descended

children.name: Canaan
children.decription: The ancestor of the Jebusites, the Amorites, Girgashites, Hivites, Arkites, Sinites, Arvadites, Zemarites, and Hamathites.
